title: Quality Zac Ganks

embed.description: Just quickly this video was made with Premiere which is different than what I normally use (Sony Vegas) so while I'm kinda transitioning to learn premiere any critique you guys have for how I can improve this editing style is appreciated :D Mr4Eva shows us his green and mean side, with crazy blobby grassy plays that put lawn mowers and green cordial flavoured jelly to shame.

body: Truly these were some quality zac ganks.
